                     <interp inst="t17900424-66-person631" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                  </persName>
            , aged 32
         </p>
               <p>GUILTY,</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t17900424-66-verdict357" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17900424-66-verdict357" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17900424-66-verdict357" type="verdictSubcategory" value="lesserOffence"></interp>
               Of stealing, but not privately
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t17900424-66-punish358" type="punishmentDescription">
