               Transported for seven years
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Tried by the first Middlesex Jury before Mr. RECORDER.</p>
               <p>Prisoner Trotter to Bixley. You have swallowed a bitter pill, and if it does not digest this time, it will digest at another time you may depend upon it.</p>
